<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hungry-adj">hungry <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'hʌŋɡri/    美 /'hʌŋɡri/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>饥饿的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>feel hungry
感到饥饿</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the hungry
饥民</p></div>

<h4 id="2-eager">2.★ <strong>渴望的 (eager)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Stay hungry, stay foolish.
求知若饥，虚心若愚！</p><footer>乔布斯</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>(be) hungry for:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The students are hungry for knowledge.
学生们求知若渴。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="go-hungry">go hungry</h3>
<p>1.<strong>挨饿：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As long as you have an ability you won't go hungry.
只要有一技之长，你就不会挨饿。</p></div></div>